  <data name="checkBoxAutoLoad.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Start/stop watching the selected directory for newly
added image files and automatically load each new
file as it appears (must set a valid directory first).</value>
  </data>
  <data name="textBoxDiectory.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Full path of the folder to monitor for new
diffraction-image files. Use the Set button to browse,
or type a path. Subfolders are watched recursively.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="buttonSetDirectory.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Browse for the folder to monitor and
put its path in the directory box.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="label1.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Full path of the folder to monitor for new
diffraction-image files. Use the Set button to browse,
or type a path. Subfolders are watched recursively.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="checkBoxNumberMatching.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Filter auto-loaded files by the trailing
number in the filename: load only when
(number mod divisor) equals/does not
equal the remainder, per the =/= toggle.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="radioButtonEqual.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Equal mode: load the file only when (trailing
number mod divisor) equals the remainder.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="radioButtonNotEqual.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Not-equal mode: load the file only when (trailing
number mod divisor) does NOT equal the remainder.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="numericBoxDivisor.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Divisor for the filename-number test: file passes
when (trailing number mod this divisor) equals the
remainder. Integer &gt;0; 0 never matches. Default 3.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="numericBoxRemainder.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Target remainder for the filename-number test: file
passes when (trailing number mod divisor) equals
this value. Integer in 0..divisor-1. Default 2.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="checkBoxKeywords.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Filter auto-loaded files by name: load
only files whose filename contains the
keyword text entered to the right.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="textBoxKeyword.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Substring that a filename must contain to
be auto-loaded (case-sensitive). Only used
when the Keyword filter checkbox is enabled.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="checkBoxAutoAfterLoad.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>When checked, automatically run the
checked steps below (auto-contrast, find
center, mask spots, get profile, macro)
every time a new image finishes loading.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="checkedListBoxAuto.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Steps run after each image loads (top to bottom):
Auto contrast (auto brightness), Find center
(beam-center detection), Mask spots (remove
single-crystal spots), Get profile (integrate
rings into a 1D 2theta profile), Execute macro.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="label2.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Select the named macro to run as the final step of the
auto-procedure (only when 'Execute macro' is checked).</value>
  </data>
  <data name="comboBoxMacro.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Choose which saved macro runs as the last
step of the sequence. Enabled only when
'Execute macro' is checked in the list above.</value>
  </data>
